2026-05-13T19:04:30.6256997Z 13    <!--
2026-05-13T19:04:30.6257587Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-13T19:04:30.6258474Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-13T19:04:30.6259661Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-13T19:04:30.6260560Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-13T19:04:30.6261506Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
